{"TopicId":213695,"ForumId":119,"TopicTitle":"VAB controls for KSP2. This might be stupid but i would like some help.","CreatedByName":"Diesel-Nuts","CreatedById":209496,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:34:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Diesel-Nuts","CreatedById":209496,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:34:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn KSP 1 to move the camera vertically.... you simply held down SHIFT and scrolled.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes ksp2 have a different key instead of shift? Cant seem to get the camera to move vertically.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EHelp?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"regex","CreatedById":70807,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:35:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHold middle mouse and pan the mouse up or down. Middle click on a part to focus the camera on it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Casellina X","CreatedById":226034,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:35:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMiddle mouse button to move the camera up/down/left/right. You can also middle click on a part to focus on it. Home button resets the view.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:35:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMiddle click and move the mouse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-27T16:36:03Z\u0022 title=\u002202/27/2023 04:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 27, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The Aziz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EDammit, third\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Diesel-Nuts","CreatedById":209496,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T17:39:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSweet,\u00A0 I\u0027ll try that when i get home!!\u00A0 Thank you guys!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Diesel-Nuts","CreatedById":209496,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-01T16:07:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you guys.... lol\u00A0 \u00A0 all good now\u00A0 \u00A0\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ECheers,\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}